.SS NAME
.PP
\f[B]mpcpluskeys\f[R] - mpcplus key bindings and usage
.SS DESCRIPTION
.PP
This man page describes the key bindings used to control the
\f[B]mpcplus\f[R] music player client.
.SS KEYS - CUSTOM
.PP
